"Completed via PostgreSQL MCP.\n\nCreated and populated these tables in the `employees` schema:\n\n- `employees.gender_statistics` — 2 rows\n- `employees.age_group_analysis` — 3 rows\n- `employees.birth_month_distribution` — 12 rows\n- `employees.hiring_year_summary` — 16 rows\n\nThe calculations use active salary records where `to_date = '9999-01-01'` to identify current employees, and age/tenure calculations use the reference date `2002-08-01`."